title: Kitties Don't Eat that! Do they?
description: Lilly is just two years old, she has a favorite kitty that she loves to take with her absolutely everywhere. The kitty even sits with her at mealtimes. Lilly is so little that she thinks that her kitty needs to try to eat everything that she eats. But kitties don't eat human food. Do they? And stuffed kitties don't even eat at all. Will Lilly ever learn how to tell the difference between live and stuffed animals? Will her kitty ever stay clean?
author: Sarah Taber
